title: J4 camps his nautilus top
body:
I kill them both at least 3 times each, most of the time during 2v1s, 

I point out that J4 must be duo with naut because he's ignoring quality ganks on his winning lanes to constantly fail with his legit bronze 5 top laner buddy

tells me that I shouldn't worry, I'll improve at the game and understand why he's doing that one day.
